info.description:
Run ABA relationship lookup use cases from the XSHI file. The agent calls POST /run with { useCase, params }; the Lambda maps each use case to its backend REST endpoint:
- xshiFileAbaGroup: GET /xshipRelationshipFile/xshipABA?abaGroup={abaGroup}
- xshiFileAba: GET /xshipRelationshipFile/xshipABA?abaNumber={abaNumber}
